  32:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/cache/class/../../../stdlib/lv_string.h ****  * @brief Copies a block of memory from a source address to a destination address.
  33:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/cache/class/../../../stdlib/lv_string.h ****  * @param dst Pointer to the destination array where the content is to be copied.
